                            },
                            "page": 306
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "related_creatures",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Related Creatures",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Related Creatures",
                        "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Other Giant Spiders",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "A staggering number of species of giant spider exist in the world. Some, like the dream spider, whose venom creates strange hallucinations, are relatively small. Others, like the lumbering ogre spider, are larger than horses.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Bestiary",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Bestiary pg. 306",
                                "alt": "Bestiary pg. 306",
                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01y0m?Pathfinder-Bestiary"
                            },
                            "page": 306
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "related_creatures",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Related Creatures",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Related Creatures",
                        "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
                    }
